{"sn1.8:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.8 ","sn1.8:0.2":"1. Nalavagga ","sn1.8:0.3":"Susammutthasutta ","sn1.8:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn1.8:1.2":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn1.8:2.1":"“Yesam dhamma susammuttha, ","sn1.8:2.2":"paravadesu niyare; ","sn1.8:2.3":"Sutta te nappabujjhanti, ","sn1.8:2.4":"kalo tesam pabujjhitun”ti. ","sn1.8:3.1":"“Yesam dhamma asammuttha, ","sn1.8:3.2":"paravadesu na niyare; ","sn1.8:3.3":"Te sambuddha sammadanna, ","sn1.8:3.4":"caranti visame saman”ti. "}